{"tid":439323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"識揾男朋友一定揾連登仔","createTime":"2017-10-17T16:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T06:16:52.000Z","uid":127705,"like":81,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c60062dda5e2b81a17ddbbf6c90e113e513295b","tid":439323,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收皮啦你班死毒撚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望都唔想望你呀<br />\n一撚日淨係識雙重標準<br />\n成日要求人地大波樣靚身材好<br />\n生得平凡d就話人咁撚樣衰話人係雞係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你拍拖就一定要扑野，<br />\n但同時又要求人地係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己現實就係一個又油頭又多暗瘡<br />\n又唔識打扮又唔係高大又要樣衰既死宅毒<br />\n又唔肯執下自己個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你自己拼埋去個條女果到都覺得肉酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n參考:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/001346_23413c8d52e629e899fff704eeeaee99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F001346_23413c8d52e629e899fff704eeeaee99.jpg&h=459f761c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">不排除有清泉</span></span>"},{"pid":"1743897ad28f69dd0740594d17bc3a5ed0759c19","tid":439323,"uid":76366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"留名睇連登仔話樓主係臭雞<br />\n<br />\nbtw正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d03bfd538582012b36fe9944c58089638b2e2a","tid":439323,"uid":127705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"最慘係佢地覺得自己完全冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabf60d4df80bda27af4cbf60889d521d07ef5bb","tid":439323,"uid":76105,"like":12,"dislike